            "@source": "Eberron: Rising from the Last War",
            "@id": "ID_WOTC_ERLW_RACIAL_TRAIT_MARK_OF_HEALING_SPELLS_OF_THE_MARK",
            "description": {
                "p": "If you have the Spellcasting or the Pact Magic class feature, the spells on the Mark of Healing Spells table are added to the spell list of your spellcasting class.",
                "h5": "Mark of Healing Spells",
